Class SettingsView

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.layout.Region
javafx.scene.layout.Pane

no.ntnu.idatx1005.view.content.SettingsView
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, ButtonClickSubject
public class SettingsView extends javafx.scene.layout.VBox implements ButtonClickSubject

View class for the settings view.

The view extends the VBox class. The view is meant to be used as a child of the

invalid reference 
ContentView
class. It implements the ButtonClickSubject interface to notify observers when a button in the view is clicked.
Since:
V1.1.0
Author:
William Holtsdalen
